00:14:44.928 --> 00:14:48.704
You know, a lot of things that we do, our church does a great job of outreach.

00:14:48.544 --> 00:14:55.936
So we provide Christmas gifts and food to many, many, many organizations and nonprofits in our community because we are called to do that.

00:14:55.744 --> 00:14:58.208
Well, you do so with joyful hearts.

00:14:58.912 --> 00:15:02.400
But sometimes we're called to do that to people that we may not agree with.

00:15:02.464 --> 00:15:04.352
That don't look like us

00:15:04.480 --> 00:15:06.688
That don't believe like us

00:15:06.912 --> 00:15:08.928
But yet we're still called.

00:15:08.896 --> 00:15:11.328
To serve and love our neighbor.

00:15:12.000 --> 00:15:13.696
And when we look at Joseph,

00:15:13.728 --> 00:15:15.328
He teaches us.

00:15:15.232 --> 00:15:19.072
That sometimes the faithful choice can be a difficult one.

00:15:19.904 --> 00:15:21.920
That when you do love.

00:15:21.792 --> 00:15:25.824
It could cost you your comfort and reputation and control.

00:15:27.328 --> 00:15:28.960
But mercy is there.

00:15:28.960 --> 00:15:31.136
Grace will meet you there.

00:15:31.040 --> 00:15:33.216
Do not be discouraged.

00:15:33.888 --> 00:15:39.008
And so when we when we leave today, reflecting upon love, think of these questions.

00:15:39.808 --> 00:15:44.576
Where is God calling me to stay in love instead of walk away?

00:15:45.920 --> 00:15:51.136
Where is love asking me to act and not just feel the warm and fuzzies?

00:15:52.064 --> 00:15:54.208
And who needs my presence?

00:15:53.984 --> 00:15:55.552
It's just my presence, right?

00:15:55.808 --> 00:15:57.376
More than my opinion.

00:15:59.488 --> 00:16:04.096
Who needs the love of Jesus Christ in this time of the year?

00:16:04.864 --> 00:16:07.936
So may we choose compassion over cruelty

00:16:07.936 --> 00:16:10.048
Obedience over fear

00:16:09.984 --> 00:16:12.544
And presence over protection.

00:16:13.600 --> 00:16:14.720
Because

00:16:14.848 --> 00:16:17.568
Love is found within the manger.

00:16:17.760 --> 00:16:20.832
Love is shown through Jesus Christ.

00:16:21.440 --> 00:16:25.184
Love is shown through faithfulness and obedience.

00:16:25.184 --> 00:16:28.128
And may we show both of that to our Lord.

00:16:27.968 --> 00:16:29.216
Into the world.

00:16:29.344 --> 00:16:30.496
Let us pray.
